data.description: Welcome to 11738 Green Coral Drive!! This Beautiful  5 Bedroom 2.5 bath home has been updated. Located in a nice stablish subdivision of Greensbrook Place. Large family room features a natural stone tile corner fireplace  and dark wood like floor tile.  The kitchen offers a gas stove, granite counter tops and island. Open Concept!  All 5 spacious bedrooms come with very nice size closets. Sizable back yard ! You do not want to miss the opportunity to see it!
